Name: Epic Lokir Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Greater Lokir Rune, Level 4 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes trickery and cunning, allowing those who channel it the ability to manipulate the conniving darkness.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following features.SPACEShroud of LiesSPACEAs an action, you summon forth a cloud of magical darkness that is centered on you in a DISTANCE10-15DISTANCE foot radius. This cloud lasts for TIME2-4TIME rounds. You can see in this magical darkness as if it were dim light.SPACESPACETrickster's IreSPACEAs an action, you speak words of malice toward a creature within DISTANCE30-45DISTANCE feet of you that can hear you. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes DAMAGE2-4DAMAGEd10 psychic damage and are blinded with rage, becoming hostile to all creatures for TIME2-4TIME turns. Whenever the target makes an attack roll, it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or choose a new target for the attack. If no other target is available, the attack automatically misses.SPACESPACETapestry of FalsehoodSPACEAs an action, you attempt to twist the mind of a creature that you can see within DISTANCE30-45DISTANCE feet of you. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or see you as an ally and their allies as foes for TIME3-5TIME rounds.SPACESPACEBackstabSPACEAs a bonus action, you conjure a dagger into your hand for TIME4-6TIME rounds and can make a melee spell attack with the dagger against a creature within reach as an action on each of your turns. On a hit, the target takes psychic damage equal to DAMAGE3-5DAMAGEd10 + your Charisma modifier and must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, you become invisible to the target until the end of your next turn.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 5 runic attunement slots. Requires Charisma 17 or greater to attune.
